  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nWhen we enable #share-context-menu in chrome://flags, \"Share\" submenu will be created in the menu when we right click omnibox. A raw webcontents pointer hold in ShareSubmenuModel and not observer it's lifecycle. If the webcontents destroyed before click \"Create QRCode..\""
